headline: Is Teradyne (TER) Pricing Reflecting Its Strong Multi Year Share Price Performance
summary: If you are wondering whether Teradyne's current share price lines up with its underlying worth, this breakdown will help you frame that question clearly before you commit fresh capital. Teradyne shares last closed at US$231.89, with returns of 1.8% over 7 days, 16.8% over 30 days, 11.7% year to date, 76.7% over 1 year, 126.6% over 3 years, and 97.3% over 5 years.
